VIN a1 0 PULSE(0 1.9253051 24.0n 0.90872975n 0.90872975n 70.0n 160.0n)
VFIX_A2 a2 0 0
VFIX_B b 0 1.9253051
XU1 a1 a2 b zn vdd vdd 0 0 gf180mcu_fd_sc_mcu7t5v0__oai21_1
